headline: How Recent Developments Are Rewriting the Story for General Mills
summary: General Mills’ consensus analyst price target has shifted only slightly, moving from $54.80 to $53.89 after recent updates. This modest change comes as analysts weigh lower-than-expected guidance and results against the company’s long-term reinvestment plans and brand strength.
